# Generated / dropped-in content. None of this is authored in-repo:
# - app/public/locations/*.webp — mirrored from World/images/ at build time
# - app/src/machine1/ — generated by app/raw2/generate_machine1.py
#
# app/raw2/World/ IS tracked: it ships as a default seed so the build
# works on a fresh clone. Kirill replaces it (or stages it as needed)
# when new authoring drops happen.
#
# NOTE: We track *.jpg files in locations/ as fallback for WebP incompatibility on some Android devices
app/public/locations/*.webp
app/src/machine1/
